["DescriptionBeautiful Five bedroom Unfurnished Villa with private pool, private party area, private car park and lift and lush surroundings located in the serene landscape of Ras al Khaimah.
Flash Real estate offers an exclusive selection of 3 to 5 bedroom Villas.We emphasises on larger living spaces to provide you with high-quality living.
An exclusive collection of luxury homes, each in a class of its own, We offers a chance to reside at the pinnacle of elegance in one of the world's most celebrated neighborhood's,Dubai which is Located only 45 minutes away from the villa , it is awe-inspiring, inside out. Right from its fluid design and sophisticated features to its unsurpassed amenities and prestigious location, it is a true jewel in our crown.
Features about the Imperial Avenue are:
- Wonderful Landscaping;
- Separated Dining and seating area outside in the garden;
- Own Swimming Pool;
- Fully Furnished Kitchen;
- Garage for 2 cars + minimum 6 cars parking spaces in front of the villa;
- Private elevator;
- Extra living area on 2nd floor;
The location within the village is close to fantastic facilities including, Al Hamra Yacht Club and Marina as well as being a short drive to Al Hamra Mall and Golf Club.
Al Hamra Village is also home to the 5* Waldorf Astoria and Ritz Carlton Hotels, offering fine dining and facilities in the community."]
